@startuml runtime-logging-architecture

title runtime-logging — 双进程架构 (electron-log v5: console 接管 + IPC bridge + file transport rotation/cleanup)

' 日常术语优先; 详细 module / 函数名 / commit / REVIEW 见 INDEX 第 3 列

package "主进程 (main)" {
  [main logger\n(utils/logger.ts, electron-log/main)] as MLog
  [errorHandler.startCatching\n(uncaught/unhandledRejection 落盘\n+ uncaughtException → app.exit(1))] as Fatal
  [file transport\n(file level=info / console level=silly)] as FT
  [LogsSection IPC\n(OpenDir / ShowInFinder / TruncateToday)] as LogsIpc
  [preload-fatal listener\n(PreloadFatalError IPC + webContents preload-error)] as PFatal
  [main 业务模块\nlog.scope('<name>')] as MBiz
}

package "渲染进程 (renderer)" {
  [renderer logger\n(utils/logger.ts, electron-log/renderer)] as RLog
  [renderer 业务模块\nlog.scope('<name>')] as RBiz
  [Settings LogsSection UI\n(3 button + logLevel 6 档下拉)] as SettingsUI
}

folder "~/Library/Logs/Agent Deck/" as Disk {
  [main-YYYY-MM-DD.log\n(按天拆 + 启动 cleanup 14 天)] as LogFile
}

' ─── main 端落盘 ───
MBiz --> MLog : logger.info/warn/error (scoped)
MLog --> FT : file transport
FT --> LogFile
Fatal --> FT : fatal 同步落盘
note right of MLog
  init order: app.setName('Agent Deck') 必先于 app.getPath('logs')
  (REVIEW_66: 否则 dev 落 ~/Library/Logs/Electron/ 撞 §不变量 1)
  console 接管: Object.assign(console, log.functions) (NODE_ENV=test 跳过保 vi.spyOn)
end note

' ─── renderer 端经 IPC bridge ───
RBiz --> RLog : logger.info/... (scoped)
RLog --> MLog : electron-log IPC bridge\n(main log.initialize() 注入 preload + __electronLog.sendToMain)
note right of RLog
  electron-log/renderer 顶层不 require electron (vitest-safe)
  console 接管守门: import.meta.env.MODE != 'test' (无 process.env §不变量 3)
end note

' ─── Settings LogsSection ───
SettingsUI --> LogsIpc : 打开目录 / Finder 显示 / 清空当天
LogsIpc --> LogFile : shell.openPath / showItemInFolder / File.clear()
SettingsUI --> MLog : logLevel 改 → setFileLevel (即改即生效; console 永 silly)

' ─── preload fatal ───
PFatal --> MLog : preload contextBridge 失败 / script 加载失败 → preload-fatal scope 落盘

note bottom of LogFile
  根本目标 (§不变量 1): macOS .app 双击启动场景 console.* 真正落盘
  (dev 终端 console transport silly 看全部; 生产靠 file transport)
  清空走 File.clear() 非 fs.truncate (同步 rotation 缓存计数, REVIEW_68 batch-2)
  + symlink 拒 (lstat)
end note

@enduml
